title: Women Artists Playing Cards
description:
Women Artists have for centuries defied convention and obstacles to achieve eminence and greatness. With all the technical virtuosity of their male equals they often surpass them in sensitivity of coloring, observing of human nature and compassion. This deck, which includes superb photographs, celebrates remarkable artists from the Renaissance to the present.
  • Dimensions: 2.63 x 0.75 x 3.63 in
  • Materials: Unique art on every card. 52 cards, 2 jokers and 1 reference card
